<paragraph blockId="5.[136,1452,266,1517]" pageId="5" pageNumber="118">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[189,721,410,436]" pageId="5" pageNumber="118">Habitat, phenology and conservation status.</emphasis>
Epiphyte. Broad-leaved evergreen lowland forests on granite at elevation of 
<quantity box="[276,389,446,473]" metricMagnitude="2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.25" metricValueMax="4.0" metricValueMin="0.5" pageId="5" pageNumber="118" unit="m" value="225.0" valueMax="400.0" valueMin="50.0">50–400 m</quantity>
a.s.l. Fl. June–July. Very rare. Suggested 
<collectionCode box="[855,923,446,472]" pageId="5" pageNumber="118">IUCN</collectionCode>
Red List status – 
<collectionCode box="[1125,1169,447,473]" country="India" lsid="urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:13033" name="Forest Research Institute, Indian Council of Forestry Research and Education" pageId="5" pageNumber="118" type="Herbarium">DD</collectionCode>
.
</paragraph>
